1
00:00:18,250 --> 00:00:27,208
[MONSTER 223A roaring]

2
00:00:27,291 --> 00:00:30,208
[LUCY] It's headin'
right for ya, Natsu!

3
00:00:30,291 --> 00:00:32,291
[NATSU]
Sweet! Leave him to me!

4
00:00:37,916 --> 00:00:41,000
[roars]

5
00:00:44,875 --> 00:00:46,875
[HAPPY]
Ha!

6
00:00:46,958 --> 00:00:49,583
[NATSU chuckles]

7
00:00:49,666 --> 00:00:51,000
[LUCY grunts]

8
00:00:52,583 --> 00:00:56,291
--[NATSU grunts]
--[MONSTER 223A groans]

9
00:00:56,375 --> 00:00:58,416
What's your rush, big guy?
Hang out'n play.

10
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:00,125
Those scales are
like a suit of armor,

11
00:01:00,208 --> 00:01:01,583
except they're tougher.

12
00:01:01,666 --> 00:01:03,958
Might take more than your
fists to break through them.

13
00:01:04,041 --> 00:01:05,750
You the expert on
breakin' stuff now?

14
00:01:05,833 --> 00:01:06,833
[LUCY]
Stand down, boys.

15
00:01:06,916 --> 00:01:08,041
[NATSU, HAPPY]
Huh?

16
00:01:08,125 --> 00:01:10,458
I've got this.
Open, Gate of the Sea-Goat!

17
00:01:10,541 --> 00:01:12,125
Capricorn!

18
00:01:18,541 --> 00:01:20,750
Greetings, M'lady.
How may I be of service?

19
00:01:20,833 --> 00:01:23,458
See that awkward-looking
crocodile monster?

20
00:01:23,541 --> 00:01:26,208
We need his scales for a client.

21
00:01:26,291 --> 00:01:27,708
A straight-forward task.

22
00:01:27,791 --> 00:01:30,250
I shall pummel him
with meticulous vigor.

23
00:01:32,333 --> 00:01:33,666
[CAPRICORN grunts]

24
00:01:33,750 --> 00:01:36,375
[MONSTER 223A groaning]

25
00:01:36,458 --> 00:01:40,416
--[CAPRICORN grunting]
--[MONSTER 223A groaning]

26
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:43,166
[LUCY] Keep it up!
You've got him on the ropes!

27
00:01:44,708 --> 00:01:46,083
Tag me in, will ya?

28
00:01:46,166 --> 00:01:48,708
Fire Dragon Iron Fist!

29
00:01:51,125 --> 00:01:54,375
[MONSTER 223A groans]

30
00:01:59,250 --> 00:02:00,375
Thank you, kind sir!

31
00:02:00,458 --> 00:02:02,708
It's been a pleasure
to serve you, as always.

32
00:02:02,791 --> 00:02:03,958
Farewell.

33
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:07,541
All right! Monster exterminated!

34
00:02:07,625 --> 00:02:10,125
They didn't tell us to
exterminate the poor guy.

35
00:02:10,208 --> 00:02:12,916
They just said that we
should take a few scales.

36
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,666
[laughs] Whatever!

37
00:02:14,750 --> 00:02:17,041
'Kay. Let's get back
to town and deliver--

38
00:02:17,125 --> 00:02:18,083
--[NATSU, HAPPY yelp]
--[rumbling]

39
00:02:18,166 --> 00:02:20,541
--[rumbling]

40
00:02:20,625 --> 00:02:22,250
[NATSU, HAPPY, LUCY gasp]

41
00:02:22,333 --> 00:02:25,083
An earthquake?

42
00:02:25,166 --> 00:02:26,875
[NATSU, HAPPY, LUCY]
Huh?

43
00:02:31,041 --> 00:02:32,458
Heads up, Natsu!

44
00:02:32,541 --> 00:02:34,333
[NATSU]
Hm?

45
00:02:34,416 --> 00:02:35,500
[LUCY, HAPPY yelp]

46
00:02:35,583 --> 00:02:36,833
Whoa, is that thing
what I think it is?

47
00:02:36,916 --> 00:02:39,958
[NATSU grunts]
A giant sky-egg!

48
00:04:14,166 --> 00:04:16,625
[ERZA]
It's been ten days?

49
00:04:16,708 --> 00:04:19,250
And I haven't seen either of
them by the guild since then.

50
00:04:19,333 --> 00:04:21,250
They said something
about warming it up.

51
00:04:21,333 --> 00:04:23,750
How warm did they say,
poached or scrambled?

52
00:04:23,833 --> 00:04:26,125
Neither one!
They're taking care of it!

53
00:04:26,208 --> 00:04:28,000
Natsu managed to
hatch Happy so I guess

54
00:04:28,083 --> 00:04:29,125
he's got a knack for this.

55
00:04:29,208 --> 00:04:31,166
Let's peek in on the nest.

56
00:04:36,125 --> 00:04:38,166
Natsu? Happy?

57
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,291
[LUCY]
Mm...

58
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,250
Hey, what the heck... happened?

59
00:04:50,791 --> 00:04:52,333
Looks like salmonella.

60
00:04:52,416 --> 00:04:54,458
They must've eaten
the whole thing raw.

61
00:04:54,541 --> 00:04:56,416
I didn't bring you
here to taunt them.

62
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:58,458
Uh? Ah?

63
00:04:58,541 --> 00:04:59,583
Whoa. What was that?

64
00:04:59,666 --> 00:05:00,750
Not sure.

65
00:05:00,833 --> 00:05:03,000
We'll find out once
I've run it through.

66
00:05:04,875 --> 00:05:06,458
[LUCY screams]

67
00:05:08,416 --> 00:05:10,833
Please don't swing
your sword at the baby.

68
00:05:10,916 --> 00:05:12,750
You okay, Natsu?

69
00:05:14,041 --> 00:05:15,958
Hey. There ya are.

70
00:05:18,208 --> 00:05:20,708
Uh, what is this thing?

71
00:05:20,791 --> 00:05:23,541
No idea, but we sure
did keep it toasty.

72
00:05:23,625 --> 00:05:25,125
It wasn't easy.

73
00:05:25,208 --> 00:05:27,958
Ten days we went
without sleeping.

74
00:05:28,041 --> 00:05:30,291
[yawns]

75
00:05:30,375 --> 00:05:32,666
It does have a certain
charm to it, up close.

76
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:34,916
Yup. I've seen uglier fur balls.

77
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,958
Wah...

78
00:05:38,291 --> 00:05:39,750
[CREATURE]
Where did I come from?

79
00:05:39,833 --> 00:05:42,625
Where am I going?
Was I born for a reason?

80
00:05:42,708 --> 00:05:44,958
My first days of life were
filled with questions,

81
00:05:45,041 --> 00:05:49,208
but instead of answers, I found
warm hands and gentle smiles.

82
00:05:49,291 --> 00:05:52,375
I found that I didn't need
to answer every question.

83
00:05:52,458 --> 00:05:54,375
That affection was enough.

84
00:05:57,583 --> 00:05:59,791
[HAPPY]
It's Kemo-Kemo!

85
00:06:16,666 --> 00:06:18,666
Wah!

86
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:20,666
All right, then! It's settled.

87
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:22,625
Your new name is Kemo-Kemo!

88
00:06:22,708 --> 00:06:24,166
Wah!

89
00:06:24,250 --> 00:06:25,291
[NATSU]
Happy?

90
00:06:25,375 --> 00:06:27,125
I'd like ya to meet
your new brother.

91
00:06:27,208 --> 00:06:29,208
Hi! I guess this means
that we're gonna have

92
00:06:29,291 --> 00:06:30,750
one more mouth to feed!

93
00:06:30,833 --> 00:06:32,708
[gasps] Hey, wait.

94
00:06:32,791 --> 00:06:35,166
D'ya think Kemo-Kemo
eats fish, or what?

95
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:36,958
[GRAY]
The signs are everywhere.

96
00:06:37,041 --> 00:06:39,125
This mystery pet spells
nothin' but trouble.

97
00:06:39,208 --> 00:06:40,333
Yeah, but,

98
00:06:40,416 --> 00:06:42,250
it seems too fluffy
to cause much damage.

99
00:06:42,333 --> 00:06:44,041
That puff could grow
into a vicious beast,

100
00:06:44,125 --> 00:06:44,750
for all we know.

101
00:06:44,833 --> 00:06:46,875
Ya think so?

102
00:06:46,958 --> 00:06:49,625
It could do anything.
We're playin' with fire, here.

103
00:06:49,708 --> 00:06:51,375
The responsible choice
would be to take it

104
00:06:51,458 --> 00:06:52,791
into the woods and leave.

105
00:06:52,875 --> 00:06:55,416
Hey, Erza. What do
you think we should do?

106
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:57,791
Get a stick. And play fetch.

107
00:06:57,875 --> 00:06:59,791
That's not what I meant,
but thanks anyway.

108
00:06:59,875 --> 00:07:02,291
[KEMO-KEMO cooing]

109
00:07:02,375 --> 00:07:05,541
[NATSU laughs]
I... gotcha now!

110
00:07:05,625 --> 00:07:06,708
[KEMO-KEMO giggles]

111
00:07:06,791 --> 00:07:07,958
Whoa, it looks like
you got me instead!

112
00:07:08,041 --> 00:07:11,250
Is this a wizard's guild
or a pet shop, I forget.

113
00:07:11,333 --> 00:07:13,750
Like I'd bring a pet
in here! This guy's kin!

114
00:07:13,833 --> 00:07:15,125
When it has an accident,

115
00:07:15,208 --> 00:07:17,291
it shall not be on
the floor of this hall.

116
00:07:17,375 --> 00:07:19,625
Besides, that dog
grows far too quickly.

117
00:07:19,708 --> 00:07:20,958
Huh?

118
00:07:21,041 --> 00:07:23,000
Yeah, he's right. Your pet
grew like two inches!

119
00:07:23,083 --> 00:07:24,333
He's not a damn pet!

120
00:07:24,416 --> 00:07:26,125
And if he makes a mess,
I'll clean it!

121
00:07:26,208 --> 00:07:28,166
Had I ever seen you
clean up after yourself,

122
00:07:28,250 --> 00:07:29,583
I'd believe you.

123
00:07:29,666 --> 00:07:30,875
[KEMO-KEMO]
Mm?

124
00:07:30,958 --> 00:07:33,416
[MAKAROV] Keep it if
you must, but not in here.

125
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:34,250
[KEMO-KEMO grunts]

126
00:07:34,333 --> 00:07:35,291
[ALL gasp]

127
00:07:35,375 --> 00:07:37,666
Kemo-Kemo! You can breathe fire!

128
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:39,166
You guys really are related!

129
00:07:39,250 --> 00:07:40,958
That's no dog. It's a hellhound.

130
00:07:41,041 --> 00:07:42,333
We should shoot it!

131
00:07:42,416 --> 00:07:44,583
I don't care what mean stuff
you say about Kemo-Kemo,

132
00:07:44,666 --> 00:07:45,791
I'm gonna keep him!

133
00:07:45,875 --> 00:07:47,875
You don't ditch family.

134
00:07:54,958 --> 00:07:55,791
[FAIRY TAIL groans]

135
00:07:55,875 --> 00:07:56,875
[MALE FT 223A]
Frog-man alert.

136
00:07:56,958 --> 00:07:58,375
[MALE FT 223B]
He's from the council

137
00:08:00,625 --> 00:08:02,125
Master Makarov.

138
00:08:02,208 --> 00:08:05,291
I've come here today as an
emissary of the Magic Council.

139
00:08:05,375 --> 00:08:08,875
[MAKAROV] Hm? Look, whatever
it is, we didn't do it.

140
00:08:08,958 --> 00:08:10,041
It's a set-up.

141
00:08:10,125 --> 00:08:11,791
I assure you, it's nothing
like that, sir.

142
00:08:11,875 --> 00:08:14,583
I've been sent to inform you of
the Council's newly established

143
00:08:14,666 --> 00:08:16,208
wizard exchange program.

144
00:08:16,291 --> 00:08:18,208
Each guild that made it
to the Grand Magic Games

145
00:08:18,291 --> 00:08:20,833
proper will send wizards to
work with each other's guild.

146
00:08:20,916 --> 00:08:22,583
The goal is to
foster co-operation

147
00:08:22,666 --> 00:08:25,083
and the sharing of
knowledge amongst you.

148
00:08:25,166 --> 00:08:27,083
A wizard exchange program?

149
00:08:27,166 --> 00:08:29,083
You may send five
wizards of your choosing.

150
00:08:29,166 --> 00:08:30,958
Hey, Gramps! Pick me, will ya?

151
00:08:31,041 --> 00:08:31,791
[gasps]

152
00:08:31,875 --> 00:08:33,041
I love to learn stuff!

153
00:08:33,125 --> 00:08:34,583
Not to mention, this'll be
the perfect chance

154
00:08:34,666 --> 00:08:36,541
for me to ask around
about Kemo-Kemo!

155
00:08:36,625 --> 00:08:38,583
Natsu. No offense,
but you don't even know

156
00:08:38,666 --> 00:08:39,916
what "exchange wizard" means.

157
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,416
Still gonna be one!
Are you comin' too, Happy?

158
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:43,666
Aye!

159
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:45,166
[LUCY]
Guess I'll go with them.

160
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:47,333
Pretty sure they'll start a
war if they're unsupervised

161
00:08:47,416 --> 00:08:47,875
[GRAY grunts]

162
00:08:47,958 --> 00:08:48,916
Going somewhere?

163
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:52,041
Uh. The bathroom,
if that's okay!

164
00:08:52,125 --> 00:08:55,291
And neglect your education?
I don't think so.

165
00:08:55,375 --> 00:08:58,958
Education my butt! You just
like to boss me around!

166
00:08:59,041 --> 00:09:01,333
You're not just cute.
You're adorable.

167
00:09:01,416 --> 00:09:03,375
Now you're ignoring me, too?

168
00:09:03,458 --> 00:09:06,333
Hey! Happy! Kemo-Kemo! Let's go!

169
00:09:06,416 --> 00:09:07,500
Aye, sir!

170
00:09:07,583 --> 00:09:09,541
[KEMO-KEMO]
Wah!

171
00:09:09,625 --> 00:09:11,208
[MAKAROV, FROG 223A]
Hm...

172
00:09:14,583 --> 00:09:19,666
[NATSU groans]
Yo, Gray. Kill me will ya?

173
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:22,666
[snoring]

174
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:25,916
It's crazy. Kemo-Kemo
just keeps on growing.

175
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:29,041
Yup. He officially
looks like a pillow.

176
00:09:29,125 --> 00:09:31,041
I'm focused on the
exchange program.

177
00:09:31,125 --> 00:09:34,541
If you wanna give the little guy
a cuddle, just go for it.

178
00:09:34,625 --> 00:09:37,541
[ICHIYA] Welcome, friends.
It's been too long.

179
00:09:37,625 --> 00:09:39,750
Man.

180
00:09:40,791 --> 00:09:42,708
Um. Thank you for having us.

181
00:09:42,791 --> 00:09:45,375
I smelled you coming
for miles, Erza.

182
00:09:45,458 --> 00:09:47,583
Having once intertwined
your parfum with my own,

183
00:09:47,666 --> 00:09:49,458
I'm attuned to your scent.

184
00:09:49,541 --> 00:09:52,375
Mmm! Best sniff I've ever had.

185
00:09:52,458 --> 00:09:53,041
[ERZA, LUCY]
Ugh...

186
00:09:53,125 --> 00:09:54,416
What does that mean?

187
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:56,833
It's difficult to convey
with mere words, sweet Lucy.

188
00:09:56,916 --> 00:09:58,000
You seem tense.

189
00:09:58,083 --> 00:09:59,458
Why don't we go to
the lounge and unwind?

190
00:09:59,541 --> 00:10:01,291
[REN] It might look like we
cleaned up because we knew

191
00:10:01,375 --> 00:10:02,583
you were coming, but we didn't.

192
00:10:02,666 --> 00:10:04,666
Uhh. Cool. So!

193
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:06,750
We're here to help and learn.
D'ya have work for us?

194
00:10:06,833 --> 00:10:08,541
Yes, though your task
is such a pleasant one,

195
00:10:08,625 --> 00:10:10,375
it hardly warrants the name.

196
00:10:10,458 --> 00:10:12,250
Hm? And you are?

197
00:10:12,333 --> 00:10:13,916
[KEMO-KEMO]
Mm?

198
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,250
This is Kemo-Kemo!

199
00:10:15,333 --> 00:10:16,541
Have you ever seen
someone like him?

200
00:10:16,625 --> 00:10:18,916
No. Sniff, sniff.

201
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:21,583
His parfum is unlike
any beast's I've smelled.

202
00:10:21,666 --> 00:10:24,083
Thanks man! I washed
him earlier today!

203
00:10:24,166 --> 00:10:25,500
I know.

204
00:10:25,583 --> 00:10:27,833
As long as he doesn't bite
our patrons, he can stay.

205
00:10:27,916 --> 00:10:29,041
What patrons?

206
00:10:29,125 --> 00:10:30,916
All right. Show them
to the dressing rooms.

207
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,250
[HIBIKI, EVE, REN, JENNY]
Right this way, please.

208
00:10:32,333 --> 00:10:34,500
[GRAY, NATSU]
Uh...

209
00:10:34,583 --> 00:10:36,750
[LUCY, ERZA]
Uh...

210
00:10:37,916 --> 00:10:39,250
Man...

211
00:10:39,333 --> 00:10:41,791
For a time, I felt true beauty
was beyond improvement.

212
00:10:41,875 --> 00:10:44,833
That was before I saw Erza
in a low cut, strapless dress.

213
00:10:44,916 --> 00:10:46,625
They're both stunning.
Well done, sir.

214
00:10:46,708 --> 00:10:48,625
Ichiya is the man!

215
00:10:48,708 --> 00:10:49,916
Ichiya is the man!

216
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,416
[HIBIKI, EVE, REN]
The girls are lookin' fine!

217
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:53,708
They're lookin' fierce.
Who showed 'em how to work it?

218
00:10:53,791 --> 00:10:58,125
[ICHIYA]
I did! Man!

219
00:10:59,166 --> 00:11:00,208
I've gotta say...

220
00:11:00,291 --> 00:11:03,000
These dresses are
rather elegant.

221
00:11:03,083 --> 00:11:04,083
[ERZA, LUCY gasp]

222
00:11:07,208 --> 00:11:07,750
Natsu!

223
00:11:07,833 --> 00:11:08,958
Whoa!

224
00:11:09,041 --> 00:11:10,625
[KEMO-KEMO]
Mm!

225
00:11:10,708 --> 00:11:13,750
[laughs] The clothes
make the man, ol' buddy.

226
00:11:13,833 --> 00:11:15,208
Shut up, frosty!

227
00:11:15,291 --> 00:11:17,125
Hush, Gray. Go find your pants.

228
00:11:17,208 --> 00:11:19,125
[GRAY]
Hm? Ah, damnit!

229
00:11:19,208 --> 00:11:20,750
[NATSU chuckles]

230
00:11:20,833 --> 00:11:22,458
Now that you're dressed,
it's time to go see

231
00:11:22,541 --> 00:11:25,208
what you can do! Your job
is to mingle with our guests.

232
00:11:25,291 --> 00:11:28,125
Go stun our clients with
your wit and beauty!

233
00:11:28,208 --> 00:11:30,958
As long as they don't
touch me. All right!

234
00:11:31,041 --> 00:11:33,125
Let's be the best
escorts we can be!

235
00:11:33,208 --> 00:11:34,541
Agreed.

236
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:46,333
[HAPPY laughs]

237
00:11:46,416 --> 00:11:48,375
[FEMALE 223A] So you're
handsome and a wizard?

238
00:11:48,458 --> 00:11:50,875
