you have a good time,

239
00:11:50,958 --> 00:11:52,000
so drink up, bucko.

240
00:11:52,083 --> 00:11:53,625
Looks like someone's
having fun.

241
00:11:53,708 --> 00:11:56,000
Yeah, but it is definitely
not the customer.

242
00:11:56,083 --> 00:11:57,916
In case you were wondering,
I'd never let

243
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,333
anyone treat me like that.

244
00:11:59,416 --> 00:12:01,125
--Hey! Take a look at this guy!
--[CUSTOMERS yelping]

245
00:12:01,208 --> 00:12:02,750
D'ya know what to feed him?

246
00:12:02,833 --> 00:12:05,041
[ICHIYA]
Ugh. Man.

247
00:12:05,125 --> 00:12:06,666
